headline: Wells Fargo lowers parcel estimates, UPS stock downgraded
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo downgraded United Parcel Service (NYSE:UPS) stock to Equal Weight from Overweight and cut its price target to $98 in a note Tuesday, citing mounting trade headwinds and execution risks across the parcel delivery industry.
